	* src/sparseQR.c: Fix thinko in sparseQR_resid_fitted.
	* tests/sparseQR.R: Added
	* man/sparseQR-class.Rd: Document methods for qr.* generics
	* R/sparseQR.R: Return correct # of coefs; fix cut-and-paste errors

